item.title: Fixing the Nulled out items so that there visible and useable. (NULL)
item.dc:creator: @heroisgay heroisgay
item.description:
@heroisgay wrote:

yermom:

Well the reason that they are null is because the server you are using need a specific client that has those items . so try downloading a new client to see if it works. or the client that the maker of the server intended you to use.

Or rather add the models & ints to your own client.
